# Frontend Web (Vite/TypeScript)

- UI is metadata-driven: dynamic forms and universal grid only.
- Entity UX lives in `src/app/entity-view.ts`; shell in `src/app/main.ts`.
- Do not create entity-specific field components; consume platform metadata API.
- ESLint + vitest run in CI (`client-lint-web` job).
- Parity with Flutter: same contract in `src/metadata/contract.ts`.
